{"tid":2390652,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬斯克宣布自己是比特幣的「支持者」 再次刺激價格上漲","createTime":"2021-02-01T16:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T08:11:10.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6947ac96756d4a56193d2cb8074b879c19265713","tid":2390652,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T16:32:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/AgzjQEbq.s3evqRXOCLNhQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/2znngTzPQwi48Ejio2FXbg--~B/aD02NzU7dz0xMjAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8106563009a15609bc77a0d690a81671\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FAgzjQEbq.s3evqRXOCLNhQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F2znngTzPQwi48Ejio2FXbg--~B%2FaD02NzU7dz0xMjAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fbloomberg_chinese_traditional_757%2F8106563009a15609bc77a0d690a81671&h=6eeec981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【彭博】-- 伊隆&middot;馬斯克公開宣布自己是比特幣的支持者後，這一最大的加密貨幣價格再起漣漪。<br />\n<br />\n這位億萬富翁在社交音頻媒體Clubhouse上表示，目前他認為「比特幣是個好東西」，還說自己參與晚了，應該在八年前就買進這種加密貨幣。<br />\n<br />\n比特幣周一在他講話時飆升至近34,500美元，後回吐部分漲幅。 它1月29日在馬斯克將自己的推特賬戶資料改成#bitcoin後一度大漲16%，觸及38,000美元。由此帶來的漲幅在周一前已近殆盡。<br />\n<br />\n最近推特和Reddit論壇帶動的散戶需求急劇波動，衝擊加密貨幣市場。以玩笑起家的狗狗幣（Dogecoin）在周末暴跌前已經躋身市值前10位的加密貨幣之列。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克在Clubhouse上表示，他對其它加密貨幣沒有很強的看法，自己對狗狗幣的評論只是開玩笑。他說：「最具諷刺意味的結果是狗狗幣將來成為地球的貨幣。」<br />\n<br />\n比特幣自1月初觸及近42,000美元的紀錄高位以來跌掉了約8,000美元，但在過去一年的漲幅依然超過260%。<br />\n<br />\n有人認為，比特幣之所以能贏得更廣泛的投資者基礎，是因為它擠壓了黃金對沖美元疲軟或通貨膨脹等風險的作用。還有人則認為，動盪的漲勢很大程度上是由刺激政策帶來的投機所推動。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克說：「比特幣真的處於被傳統金融人士廣泛接受的邊緣。」"},{"pid":"983118918016a16b81cd9a93460a3f62739cc029","tid":2390652,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T16:36:39.000Z","msg":"我dllm臭閪，依家唔洗打機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"932d125db84d9085f6e02de84c75a18771c7e392","tid":2390652,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"983118918016a16b81cd9a93460a3f62739cc029","tid":2390652,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T16:36:39.000Z","msg":"我dllm臭閪，依家唔洗打機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T07:52:15.000Z","msg":"你去屌鳩AMD同Nvidia產能太低仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ebd11dc5b46b78f019a3eacf9a5eb9cfd69fab","tid":2390652,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:11:10.000Z","msg":"條閪佬靠出口術賺到嘅錢仲多過賣車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}